    <!-- ═══ SELECTION GUIDE ═══ -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface" aria-labelledby="selection-heading">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="section-label text-accent mb-4">Selection Guide</div>
        <h2 id="selection-heading" class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-800 text-ink tracking-wide uppercase mb-8">
          Selecting Bakery <span class="text-accent">Conveyors</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-5">
          <p>
            Specify bakery conveyors by answering these questions for each production stage:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-4 ml-2">
            <li><strong class="text-ink">What is the product?</strong> Bread, cookies, crackers, pastries, or snacks? Each has different fragility, temperature, and handling requirements.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink">What is the throughput?</strong> Products per minute, lane count, and line speed determine conveyor width, speed, and motor sizing.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink">What is the temperature range?</strong> Oven bands need high-temp metal belts. Cooling conveyors need airflow-permeable mesh. Packaging conveyors run at ambient.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink">What floor space is available?</strong> Limited floor space drives spiral solutions over straight-line conveyors.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink">What cleaning method is required?</strong> Allergen-critical lines need tool-free belt removal and COP capability. Non-allergen lines may use dry brush cleaning.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink">What packaging equipment connects downstream?</strong> Wrapper infeed speed, bagger loading method, and <a href="/industries/packaging-line-conveyors/case/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-semibold">case packer</a> requirements determine conveyor output specifications.</li>
          </ol>
          <p>
            For budgeting guidance, see the <a href="/resources/conveyor-cost-guide/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-semibold">conveyor cost guide</a>. Bakery conveyors range from $$ for simple ambient belt sections to $$$$ for spiral cooling systems with environmental controls.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>

