            <p>Bakeries use cooling spiral conveyors, oven band conveyors, proofing conveyors, depositor infeed belts, pan conveyors, and <a href="/industries/packaging-line-conveyors/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-semibold">packaging line conveyors</a>. Each production stage requires different belt materials, temperature ratings, and speed controls.</p>
