          <div class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>Wire mesh belts (stainless for ovens, carbon steel for cooling), modular plastic (acetal or polypropylene for ambient handling), polyurethane (FDA-compliant direct food contact), and silicone (non-stick for sticky doughs). Selection depends on temperature, product type, and food contact requirements.</p>
