          <div class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>Bakery conveyors meet food safety through BISSC certification, FDA-compliant contact materials, open-frame construction for cleaning access, and tool-free belt removal. BISSC standards address cleanability, material selection, and hygienic design specific to baking equipment. See <a href="/industries/food-conveyors/sanitary/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-semibold">sanitary conveyor standards</a> for more detail.</p>
